%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20French-trained%20brigade%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20flagship%20project.%20Now%20its%20ex-commander%20is%20on%20bail%20for%20%242.1%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227396%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20artillerymen%20in%20the%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20load%20a%20self-propelled%20Caesar%20howitzer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6791dfd810c98eace913941e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225278%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20is%20equipped%20with%20French%20weaponry%20like%20the%20self-propelled%20Caesar%20howitzer%20but%20has%20suffered%20from%20scandal%20since%20before%20it%20was%20deployed%20on%20the%20front%20lines.%3Cp%3EGENYA%20SAVILOV%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ex-commander%20of%20the%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20with%20bail%20set%20at%20%242.1%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECol.%20Dmytro%20Ryumshin%20led%20the%20%26quot%3BAnne%20of%20Kyiv%26quot%3B%20brigade%20until%20stepping%20down%20abruptly%20in%20December.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20unit%20was%20hyped%20as%20French-trained%20but%20has%20faced%20reports%20of%20mass%20desertion%20before%20deploying.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20court%20in%20Kyiv%20has%20set%20bail%20for%20Col.%20Dmytro%20Ryumshin%2C%20the%20recently%20replaced%20commander%20of%20Ukraine's%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%2C%20at%20%242.1%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20lawyer%2C%20Bohdan%20Zabara%2C%20told%20Ukrainian%20broadcaster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsuspilne.media%2F931291-sud-vidpraviv-pid-vartu-ekskombriga-155-i-ombr-anna-kiivska-rumsina%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwY2xjawH-Fu5leHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZPI7IF_hk6tH8h_GRSGpVYIRQ3UfPLgfZ3ZvdXU6RjwVZS0fWlQvdVIFQ_aem_tVD7cEytl0s_XoJsXxW6WQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESuspilne%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20court's%20decision%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20Ukraine%20probes%20a%20series%20of%20scandals%20that%20have%20marred%20the%20combat%20debut%20of%20the%20155th%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20brigade%20partially%20trained%20in%20France%20and%20equipped%20with%20modern%20French%20weaponry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicknamed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-brigade-armed-french-tanks-artillery-about-to-enter-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAnne%20of%20Kyiv%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20an%2011th-century%20Kyiv%20princess%20who%20became%20a%20French%20queen%2C%20it%20was%20touted%20as%20a%20way%20for%20Europe%20to%20directly%20strengthen%20Ukraine's%20starved%20manpower.%20But%20the%20brigade's%20reputation%20soured%20at%20home%20as%20local%20journalists%20reported%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-investigate-155th-mechanized-brigade-france-anne-kyiv-desertion-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinually%20suffered%20from%20mass%20desertion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20being%20picked%20apart%20to%20reinforce%20other%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reporter%2C%20Yuriy%20Butusov%2C%20estimated%20that%201%2C700%20men%20had%20gone%20AWOL%20before%20the%20155th%20was%20sent%20into%20battle%2C%20including%20about%2050%20men%20who%20deserted%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyumshin%20oversaw%20the%20155th%20as%20it%20prepared%20to%20deploy%20on%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20but%20suddenly%20announced%20his%20resignation%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20investigators%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbr.gov.ua%2Fnews%2Fdbr-zatrimalo-kolishnogo-komandira-155-ombr-imeni-anni-kiivskoi-za-yakogo-szch-u-brigadi-nabulo-masovogo-harakteru%3Ffbclid%3DIwY2xjawH7LJlleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHTL4YTFm6o-YQ8ah00JiLPlJ9Jd7XdbHuK1luKg7SHg69WCND7BKwV2ruQ_aem_y2I6TQr7fAE3o6SAToyJ1g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0him%20on%20Monday%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsystematic%20concealment%26quot%3B%20of%20desertion%20among%20his%20troops.%20The%20State%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20said%20Ryumshin%20received%20both%20verbal%20and%20written%20reports%20of%20discipline%20issues%2C%20but%20had%20neither%20notified%20higher%20authorities%20nor%20acted%20upon%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20commander's%20actions%2C%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20were%20unable%20to%20initiate%20the%20legal%20procedure%20to%20search%20for%20and%20return%20servicemen%20to%20their%20military%20unit%20and%20reserve%20battalions%2C%20or%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20ensure%20that%20they%20served%20their%20sentences%20for%20the%20crimes%20they%20committed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyumshin's%20lawyer%2C%20Zabara%2C%20told%20Suspilne%20that%20the%20colonel%20would%20contest%20the%20bail%20amount%20set%20by%20authorities%20in%20Kyiv.%20Should%20he%20fail%20to%20meet%20bail%2C%20he%20must%20serve%2060%20days%20in%20detention%20before%20his%20closed-door%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZabara%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20comment%20request%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20155th's%20social%20media%20accounts%20show%20that%20its%20men%20are%20now%20fighting%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-pokrovsk-offensive-combat-vehicles-losses-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPokrovsk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Russia%20has%20been%20pushing%20slowly%20but%20relentlessly%20to%20capture%20the%20key%20strategic%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brigade%20is%20equipped%20with%2018%20AMX%2010%20armored%20vehicles%2C%2018%20truck-mounted%20Caesar%20howitzers%2C%20and%20128%20armored%20troop%20carriers.%20It%20enjoyed%20a%20relatively%20high%20profile%20while%20training%20in%20France%2C%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffrance-ukraine-russia-macron-training-nato-261312057c4d8253ec2c6c4b947be089%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeeting%20its%20troops%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20October%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20looks%20like%20Europe%20isn't%20done%20with%20these%20joint%20training%20programs.%20The%20European%20Union%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F11%2F08%2Fukraine-council-extends-the-mandate-of-the-eu-military-assistance-mission-for-two-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallocated%20%24425%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20training%20more%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20until%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20including%2015%2C000%20by%20the%20winter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20home%2C%20the%20155th's%20reputation%20is%20still%20shaky.%20Some%20fighters%20and%20analysts%20in%20Ukraine%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20for%20Kyiv%20to%20make%20brand-new%20brigades%20like%20the%20155th%20instead%20of%20replenishing%20older%2C%20more%20experienced%20units%20that%20were%20already%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESerhii%20Sternenko%2C%20a%20well-known%20Ukrainian%20lawyer%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-dronemakers-war-unwinnable-dirt-cheap-crowdfunding-veterans-civilians-russia-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovides%20crowdfunded%20drones%20to%20military%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20his%20organization%20was%20assisting%20the%20155th%20because%20the%20brigade%20lacked%20officially%20provided%20drones%20and%20jammers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20create%20a%20new%20brigade%20when%20existing%20brigades%20are%20critically%20understaffed%2C%20only%20to%20later%20divide%20it%20and%20transfer%20personnel%20to%20the%20old%20brigades%3F%20What's%20the%20point%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fssternenko%2F38186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20early%20January%20on%20his%20Telegram%20channel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20155th%20geared%20up%20to%20enter%20the%20fray%2C%20its%20men%20were%20also%20often%20siphoned%20off%20by%20other%20brigades%20in%20desperate%20need%2C%20leaving%20the%20French-trained%20force%20to%20haphazardly%20reassign%20its%20troops%20to%20positions%20they%20didn't%20train%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESergey%20Filimonov%2C%20commander%20of%20Ukraine's%20108th%20Battalion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pravda.com.ua%2Fcolumns%2F2025%2F01%2F10%2F7492889%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20January%2010%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20knew%20of%20about%20%26quot%3B10%20such%20brigades%20operating%20under%20these%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Western%20training%20methods%2C%20while%20provided%20by%20NATO%20troops%2C%20%26quot%3Boften%20fail%20to%20align%20with%20the%20realities%20of%20modern%20warfare%26quot%3B%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20realities%20of%20modern%20warfare%20show%20that%20foreign%20training%2C%20unless%20adapted%20to%20Ukrainian%20conditions%20and%20integrated%20with%20unit%20practices%2C%20is%20not%20only%20ineffective%20but%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20opinion%20piece%20published%20by%20Ukrainska%20Pravda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20leaders%20appear%20to%20be%20listening.%20Butusov%2C%20the%20journalist%20who%20broke%20the%20news%20about%20desertion%20in%20the%20155th%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgG3RNBoRVs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20on%20January%2012%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20had%20ordered%20for%20all%20freshly%20mobilized%20troops%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20existing%20brigades%20instead%20of%20being%20assigned%20to%20newly%20formed%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20U