0has%20been%20arrested.%20That%20person%20had%20come%20from%20Bangladesh...%20everyone%20has%20an%20attraction%20towards%20Mumbai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20needed%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Bangladesh%20after%20seeing%20Mumbai%20(but)%20needed%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%20suggesting%20Shehzad%20may%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20steal%20cash%20to%20buy%20a%20ticket%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan's%20nanny%20had%20said%20Shehzad%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20when%20confronted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khans-attacker-demanded-rs-1-crore-at-his-house-7488346%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAttacker%20Entered%20Room%20Of%20Saif's%20Son%20Jeh%2C%20Wanted%20Rs%201%20Crore%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20yesterday%2C%20when%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20going%20home%2C%20looking%20at%20his%20health%20and%20clothes%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20guess%20he%20was%20attacked%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20But%20what%20happened%20was%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn't%20just%20Nitesh%20Rane%20making%20such%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20who%20was%20with%20the%20Congress%20before%20switching%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20the%20way%20Saif%20came%20out...%20it%20seemed%20nothing%20happened%20six%20days%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20was%20attacked%2C%20the%20police%20believe%2C%20by%20Shariful%20Shehzad%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20national%20living%20illegally%20in%20India.%20The%20cops%20also%20believe%20Shehzad%2C%20who%20said%20he%20didn't%20know%20he%20was%20in%20the%20actor's%20home%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20burgle%20it%20when%20he%20was%20confronted%2C%20first%20by%20the%20nanny%20and%20then%20Mr%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehzad%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20is