or-50-million-over-alleged-sexual-assault-tapes%2Famp_articleshow%2F117478665.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Mohammad%20Amir's%20'Pushpa'%20celebration%20in%20ILT20%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737615355000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117479544%2Cimgsize-30032.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-mohammad-amirs-pushpa-celebration-in-ilt20%2Farticleshow%2F117479573.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'Pushpa'%20celebration%2C%20inspired%20by%20Allu%20Arjun's%20movie%2C%20has%20become%20a%20trend%20in%20cricket%2C%20adopted%20by%20players%20like%20David%20Warner%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20Amir.%20Amir%20showcased%20the%20move%20in%20the%20ILT20%20tournament%2C%20leading%20Desert%20Vipers%20to%20a%2010-wicket%20victory%20and%20earning%20Man%20of%20the%20Match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-mohammad-amirs-pushpa-celebration-in-ilt20%2Farticleshow%2F117479573.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20Partition%20Shaped%20Independent%20India's%20First%20Three%20Budgets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20horrors%20of%20India's%20Partition%20in%201946%20were%20deeply%20traumatic.%20Nearly%201.8%20crore%20people%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%2C%201.2%20crore%20became%20refugees%2C%20and%20approximately%2010%20lakh%20lives%20were%20lost.%20Such%20cataclysmic%20events%20were%20bound%20to%20affect%20the%20polity%2C%20economy%2C%20and%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20impacted%20regions%20for%20years%20to%20come.%20A%20paper%20from%20Princeton%20University%20concludes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20top%20decile%20of%20affected%20districts%20in%20each%20country%20experienced%20dramatic%20changes%20in%20its%20literacy%20rates%2C%20occupation%20structure%20and%20gender%20ratios%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChanges%20in%20gender%20ratios%20and%20occupational%20structures%2C%20along%20with%20many%20other%20factors%2C%20turned%20lives%20upside%20down.%20These%20life-altering%20shifts%2C%20which%20seemed%20to%20come%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20gave%20rise%20to%20thousands%20of%20stories%E2%80%94mostly%20tragic%2C%20but%20some%20filled%20with%20bravery%2C%20camaraderie%20and%20pure%20humanity.%20Such%20stories%20were%20poignantly%20depicted%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EPinjar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGaram%20Hawa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ETrain%20to%20Pakistan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20the%20two%20parts%20of%20%3Cem%3EGadar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EKalank%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20%3Cem%3EGaram%20Hawa%3C%2Fem%3E%20focused%20on%20a%20Muslim%20businessman's%20dilemma%20about%20whether%20to%20stay%20in%20India%20or%20migrate%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20%3Cem%3EPinjar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehighlighted%20the%20trials%20of%20a%20happily%20engaged%20woman%20whose%20life%20was%20shattered%20after%20being%20kidnapped%20by%20a%20man%20of%20a%20different%20religion%20during%20the%20traumatic%20events%20leading%20to%20the%20Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%201947%20Budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20this%2C%20what%20caught%20my%20attention%20was%20how%20the%20tragedy%20of%20such%20epic%20proportions%20was%20addressed%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20post-Independence%20India.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20to%20do%20so%20other%20than%20looking%20at%20budget%20announcements.%20I%20looked%20at%20three%20budget%20documents%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20numbers%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20one%20from%201947-48.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20budget%20of%20Independent%20India%20described%20the%20Partition%20(1947-48)%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20poignant%20human%20tragedy%E2%80%9D%20outside%20of%20war.%20To%20understand%20how%20it%20was%20tackled%2C%20let's%20look%20at%20the%20allocations%20made%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%20Of%20the%20total%20non-defence%20expenditure%20planned%20for%20the%20year%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20104.5%20crore%2C%20Rs%2027%20crore%20was%20earmarked%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%2C%20Rs%2012%20crore%20for%20health%20and%20education%2C%20and%20Rs%2022%20crore%20for%20pension%20and%20interest%20payments.%20Consider%20the%20attention%20it%20received%3A%2026%25%20of%20the%20total%20non-defence%20expenditure%2C%20that%20is%2C%20more%20than%20twice%20the%20amount%20allocated%20for%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20medical%20services%20combined!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year's%20budget%20(1948-49)%20made%20these%20observations%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dislocation%20caused%20by%20the%20mass%20migration%20of%20people%20between%20Western%20Pakistan%20and%20India%20remains%20to%20be%20surmounted%2C%20and%20only%20the%20fringe%20of%20the%20problem%20of%20rehabilitating%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20have%20crossed%20over%20to%20India%20has%20so%20far%20been%20addressed%E2%80%A6%20The%20budget%20for%20next%20year%20provides%20a%20substantial%20amount%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%2C%20and%20the%20House%20may%20rest%20assured%20that%20everything%20possible%20will%20be%20done%20to%20place%20these%20refugees%20in%20useful%20occupations%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerous%20Provisions%20For%20Relief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20statement%20of%20intent%2C%20backed%20by%20funds.%20A%20sum%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20was%20allocated%E2%80%94Rs%2010%20crore%20for%20rehabilitation%2C%20Rs%2010%20crore%20to%20establish%20the%20Rehabilitation%20Finance%20Administration%2C%20and%20Rs%205%20crore%20for%20loans%20and%20advances%20related%20to%20rehabilitation.%20This%20Rs%2025%20crore%20accounted%20for%2018%25%20of%20the%20country's%20planned%20non-defence%20expenditure%20at%20the%20time.%20For%20context%2C%20the%20total%20planned%20expenditure%20for%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20medical%20services%20was%20Rs%2020.9%20crore%2C%20while%20pension%20and%20debt%20servicing%20liabilities%20stood%20at%20Rs%2043.8%20crore%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20ended%20up%20spending%20Rs%2019.45%20crore%20on%20rehabilitation%20in%201948-49%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20budgeted%20Rs%2010%20crore.%20The%201949-50%20budget%20document%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9COf%20the%20total%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%20165.16%20crore%20provided%20in%20the%20budget%2C%20Rs%2052.82%20crore%20is%20accounted%20for%20by%20expenditure%20on%20refugees%2C%20food%20subsidies%2C%20and%20pre-partition%20payments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20I'm%20making%20is%20that%20the%20first%20three%20budgets%20of%20Independent%20India%20made%20generous%20provisions%20for%20addressing%20the%20wounds%20of%20Partition.%20In%20today's%20terms%2C%2026%25%20of%20the%20total%20non-defence%20expenditure%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20huge%20sum%20that%20can%20take%20care%20of%20many%20problems.%20No%20wonder%20we%20are%20familiar%20with%20several%20resettlement%20colonies%20that%20went%20on%20to%20become%20growth%20engines%20of%20Independent%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20The%20Right%20Lessons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20view%20these%20events%20in%20two%20ways.%20One%20perspective%20is%20that%20the%20Partition%20was%20a%20tragedy%20of%20epic%20proportions%2C%20and%20the%20government%20did%20what%20it%20could%20to%20alleviate%20the%20immense%20hardships%20faced%20by%20the%20people.%20However%2C%20sceptics%20might%20argue%20that%20by%20neglecting%20crucial%20areas%20like%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20for%20three%20long%20years%2C%20the%20government%20limited%20the%20growth%20potential%20of%20the%20economy%20in%20subsequent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20pick%20your%20side%3B%20I%20will%20pick%20none.%20All%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%20that%20we%20have%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20what%20led%20to%20the%20horrors%20of%20Partition%20and%20the%20toll%20it%20took%20on%20a%20young%20country%E2%80%94not%20only%20in%20the%20years%20when%20the%20carnage%20unfolded%20on%20the%20streets%20but%20also%20in%20the%20years%20that%20followed.%20Can%20we%20learn%20the%20right%20lessons%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20reflect%20on%20this%20until%20the%20next%20budget%20is%20announced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737615300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fd0m1mel8_partition_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-numbers-how-partition-shaped-independent-indias-first-three-budgets-7538703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20budget%20of%20Independent%20India%20described%20the%20Partition%20(1947-48)%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20poignant%20human%20tragedy%26quot%3B%20outside%20of%20war.%20Of%20the%20total%20non-defence%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%20104.5%20crore%2C%20Rs%2027%20crore%20was%20earmarked%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-numbers-how-partition-shaped-independent-indias-first-three-budgets-7538703%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Relief%20for%20WhatsApp%20as%20Indian%20tribunal%20suspends%20CCI's%205-yr%20data-sharing%20ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737614976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclat-suspends-whatsapp-meta-data-sharing-ban-cci-targeted-advertising-125012300538_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22