0social%20media%20platform%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20positioning%20himself%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20right-hand%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Musk's%20animosity%20towards%20Wikipedia%20may%20focus%20outwardly%20on%20the%20hand%20gesture%2C%20Wikipedia's%20goal%20of%20factual%20neutrality%20makes%20it%20a%20natural%20adversary%20to%20X%2C%20a%20platform%20increasingly%20synonymous%20with%20heated%20culture%20wars%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWikipedia%20and%20the%20media%20at%20large%20--%20which%20Musk%20has%20increasingly%20criticized%20--%20also%20pose%20a%20threat%20by%20holding%20him%20accountable%20as%20he%20thrusts%20himself%20into%20the%20center%20of%20US%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20December%20interview%20with%20New%20York%20magazine's%20Intelligencer%2C%20Wales%20said%20the%20aim%20at%20Wikipedia%20is%20for%20editors%20to%20create%20content%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bclear%20and%20acknowledges%20the%20different%20viewpoints%20out%20there%26quot%3B%20even%20amid%20%26quot%3Bthe%20rise%20in%20divisive%20feelings%2C%20partisanship%2C%20culture%20wars%2C%20all%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20site%20is%20regarded%20as%20generally%20reliable%20despite%20being%20written%20by%20a%20community%20of%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dustup%20between%20Musk%20and%20Wales%20began%20after%20the%20billionaire%20raised%20eyebrows%20Monday%20with%20his%20gesticulation%20at%20a%20Trump%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20a%20crowd%20for%20returning%20Trump%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Musk%20tapped%20the%20left%20side%20of%20his%20chest%20with%20his%20right%20hand%20and%20then%20extended%20his%20arm%20with%20his%20palm%20open.%20He%20then%20turned%20around%20to%20the%20crowd%20behind%20him%20and%20did%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20both%20Musk's%20biographical%20Wikipedia%20page%20as%20well%20as%20the%20page%20on%20the%20%