have%20eight-hour%20shifts.%20We%20have%20two-three%20shifts%20and%20the%20standard.%20So%2C%20you%20know%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20operate%20a%20company%2C%20let's%20say%2C%20from%20a%20CEO's%20point%20of%20view%2C%20you%20have%20different%20shifts.%20You%20employ%20more%20people.%20So%2C%20we%20start%20at%207.30%20in%20the%20morning...%20And%20then%20at%204%20o'clock%2C%20that%20shift%20ends%20and%20the%20next%20one%20takes%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20humanly%20possible%26quot%3B%20for%20people%20to%20be%20productive%20beyond%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20hours%2C%20the%20Serum%20Institute%20CEO%20said%20crisis%20situations%20were%20different.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20crisis%20or%20in%20an%20opportunity%2C%20your%20adrenaline%20is%20pumping.%20During%20Covid%2C%20there%20were%20nights%20where%20I%20hardly%20got%20three%20or%20four%20hours%20of%20sleep%20because%20you%20were%20talking%20to%20so%20many%20people.%20But%20that's%20not%20something%20that%20is%20sustainable.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWork%20life%20balance%20has%20been%20a%20key%20talking%20point%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20after%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%20chairman%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%20spoke%20about%20a%2090-hour%20workweek.%20During%20an%20internal%20interaction%2C%20Mr%20Subrahmanyan%20was%20asked%20why%20L%26amp%3BT%20required%20its%20employees%20to%20work%20on%20Saturdays.%20He%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20regret%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20make%20you%20work%20on%20Sundays%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20If%20I%20can%20make%20you%20work%20on%20Sundays%2C%20I%20will%20be%20more%20happy%2C%20because%20I%20work%20on%20Sundays%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20sitting%20at%20home%3F%20How%20long%20can%20you%20stare%20at%20your%20wife%3F%20How%20long%20can%20the%20wives%20stare%20at%20their%20husbands%3F%20Get%20to%20the%20office%20and%20start%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2