%2Farticleshow%2F117473958.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Open%20To%20%26quot%3BLegitimate%20Return%26quot%3B%20Of%20Indians%20Living%20Illegally%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20has%20clarified%20India's%20stance%2C%20saying%20that%20New%20Delhi%20is%20open%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%20return%26quot%3B%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20living%20'illegally'%20abroad%2C%20including%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20taken%20the%20view%20that%20if%20there%20are%20any%20of%20our%20citizens%2C%20who%20are%20not%20here%20legally%2C%20if%20we%20are%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20our%20citizens%2C%20we%20have%20always%20been%20open%20to%20their%20legitimate%20return%20to%20India.%20So%20it's%20not%20a%20position%20unique%20to%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20EAM%20Jaishankar%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20Wednesday%20(local%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20affirmed%20that%20India's%20position%20on%20the%20issue%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bprincipled%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20did%20clearly%20convey%20this%20to%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20right%20now%20that%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20debate%20going%20on%20and%20a%20resulting%20sensitivity%20which%20is%20there.%20But%20we%20have%20been%20consistent%2C%20we%20have%20been%20very%20principled%20about%20it%2C%20and%20that%20remains%20our%20position%2C%20and%20I%20conveyed%20that%20very%20clearly%20to%20US%20State%20Secretary%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEAM%20Jaishankar%2C%20however%2C%20also%20emphasised%20that%20India%20is%20very%20much%20supportive%20of%20'legal%20mobility'%20between%20two%20countries%20and%20wants%20Indian%20skills%20and%20talent%20to%20have%20great%20opportunity%20at%20the%20global%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20India%20is%20firmly%20opposed%20to%20illegal%20migration%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Breputationally%20good%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20leads%20to%20several%20illegal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20government%2C%20we%20obviously%20are%20very%20much%20supportive%20of%20legal%20mobility%20because%20we%20do%20believe%20in%20a%20global%20workplace.%20We%20want%20Indian%20talent%20and%20Indian%20skills%20to%20have%20the%20maximum%20opportunity%20at%20a%20global%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20also%20very%20firmly%20opposed%20to%20illegal%20mobility%20and%20illegal%20migration.%20because%20you%20also%20know%20that%20when%20something%20illegal%20happens%2C%20many%20other%20illegal%20activities%20get%20joined%20into%20it...%20this%20is%20not%20desirable.%20It's%20certainly%20not%20reputationally%20good...%20So%20we%20have%20with%20every%20country%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20no%20exception%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20during%20his%20meeting%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20long%20waiting%20period%20for%20getting%20US%20visas%2C%20and%20said%20it%20is%20not%20serving%20the%20relationship%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20told%20him%20(Rubio)%20that%2C%20while%20we%20understand%20all%20of%20this%2C%20and%20I%20also%20accept%20that%20these%20are%20autonomous%20processes%2C%20it%20is%20in%20our%20mutual%20interest%20to%20facilitate%20legal%20and%20mutually%20beneficial%20mobility.%20If%20it%20takes%20400%20odd%20days%20waiting%20period%20to%20get%20a%20visa%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20relationship%20is%20well%20served%20by%20this.%20So%20I%20think%20he%20also%20noted%20that%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEAM%20Jaishankar%20represented%20India%20at%20the%20US%20Preside