h%20the%20power%20of%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20now%20on%2C%20there%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20'man'%20and%20a%20'woman'%2C%20but%20'individual'%20and%20'individual'%20who%20are%20equal%20'spouses'.%20I%20congratulate%20you%20wholeheartedly%20on%20your%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2030%20countries%20have%20legalised%20marriage%20for%20all%20since%20the%20Netherlands%20became%20the%20first%20to%20allow%20same-sex%20unions%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThai%20activists%20have%20been%20pushing%20for%20same-sex%20marriage%20rights%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20with%20their%20advocacy%20stalled%20by%20political%20turbulence%20in%20a%20country%20regularly%20upended%20by%20coups%20and%20mass%20street%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKevin%20Pehthai%20Thanomkhet%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20trans%20man%2C%20married%20his%20wife%2C%20Maple%20Nathnicha%20Klintgaworn%2C%2039.%20His%2065-year-old%20father%20Phornchai%20was%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20happy%2C%20like%2C%20oh%20my%20god...%20my%20heart%20is%20beating%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20happy%20for%20this...%20I%20have%20always%20accepted%20(him)%2C%26quot%3B%20Phornchai%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhatsoever%2C%20it%20is%20OK%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPloynaplus%20Chirasukorn%20said%20she%20had%20been%20with%20her%20partner%20Kwanporn%20Kongpetch%20for%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20LGBTQ%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20monster%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20supports%20the%20push%20for%20gender%20identity%20recognition%20beyond%20biological%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20person%20who%20was%20born%20different%20sex%20from%20what%20they%20want%20to%20be%20feels%20like%20a%20person%20who%20has%20no%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20push%20for%20it%2C%20we%20will%20feel%20like%20it%20is%20really%20