3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20and%20cofounder%20John%20Mills%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20app%20received%202.5%20million%20downloads%20and%2012%20million%20active%20users%20in%20the%20past%20two%20weeks.%20Watch%20Duty%20shot%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Apple's%20app%20stores%20in%20the%20first%20days%20of%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMills%20said%20that's%20no%20reason%20to%20start%20charging%20more%20for%20Watch%20Duty's%20services%20or%20try%20to%20further%20monetize%20from%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20do%20this%20for%20the%20greater%20good%2C%20and%20the%20best%20way%20I%20found%20to%20do%20that%20is%20to%20use%20the%20nonprofit%20angle%2C%26quot%3B%20Mills%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatch%20Duty%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202021%2C%20has%20no%20brick-and-mortar%20HQ%2C%20and%20its%20staff%20all%20work%20remotely.%20Mills%20himself%20has%20a%20background%20in%20tech%20and%20co-founded%20an%20operations%20platform%20for%20chain%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20he%20was%20motivated%20to%20start%20the%20organization%20shortly%20after%20he%20moved%20to%20Sonoma%20County%20in%202020%2C%20the%20same%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-wildfires-before-and-after-photos-show-damage-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20saw%20a%20record-number%20wildfires%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Walbridge%20Fire%20in%20Sonoma%20alone%20burned%20more%20than%2055%2C000%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Walbridge%20Fire%20was%20the%20ultimate%20one%20that%20really%20got%20me%20to%20do%20something%20about%20this%2C%20and%20that%20was%20the%20one%20that%20ended%20about%20a%20quarter%20mile%20from%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20evacuated%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20I%20spent%20seven%20nights%20just%20up%20all%20day%2C%20all%20night%2C%20trying%20to%20learn%20about%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%20how%20to%20help%2C%20and%20what%20the%20problems%20were.%20It%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20this%20was%20not%20going%20to%20get%20resolved%20any%20other%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20advantage%20Watch%20Duty%20has%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20restricted%20by%20boundaries%20or%20jurisdictions%20unlike%20government%20agencies%2C%20which%20could%20slow%20down%20the%20speed%20of%20updates%20and%20emergency%20notifications%2C%20Mills%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20challenging%20because%20one%20county%20might%20have%20more%20advanced%20systems%20and%20the%20other%20one%20doesn't%2C%20but%20the%20fire%20is%20tearing%20through%20multiple%20counties%20at%20a%20time%2C%20Mills%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20one%20integrated%20system%20that%20really%20helps%20tie%20all%20this%20together%20and%20that's%20really%20where%20we%20shine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202024%2C%20according%20to%20its%20annual%20report%2C%20Watch%20Duty%20grew%20its%20yearly%20active%20users%20to%207.2%20million%20people.%20The%20app%20provides%20updates%20across%2022%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20regular%20users%2C%20Watch%20Duty%20remains%20free.%20Some%20can%20pay%20%2425%20a%20year%20for%20extra%20features%20such%20as%20flight%20tracking%20data.%20The%20organization%20has%20even%20started%20to%20build%20and%20sell%20government%20services%2C%20%26quot%3Balbeit%20very%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20Mills%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20laugh.%20They%20say%20you%20should%20charge%20more.%20I'm%20like%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20point%2C%20man.%20This%20is%20my%20life.%20I%20live%20in%20the%20woods.%20We're%20going%20to%20make%20money%2C%20but%20the%20money%20is%20to%20support%20the%20free%20operation%20and%20pay%20our%20engineers%20and%20our%20reporters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20nonprofit%2C%20Watch%20Duty%20can%20accept%20donations.%20Tech%20CEOs%20including%20Snap's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevan-spiegel-ceo-co-fo