dvertising%2C%20which%20they%20expect%20to%20fuel%20Netflix's%20next%20wave%20of%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20launched%20the%20ads%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20which%20costs%20%248%20a%20month%20after%20a%20%241%20price%20increase%20this%20week%20%E2%80%94%20in%20November%202022.%20The%20company%20said%20in%20November%20that%20the%20ad%20tier%20had%20reached%2070%20million%20global%20users.%20It%20said%20in%20its%20earnings%20release%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20ad%20plan%20makes%20up%20over%2055%25%20of%20new%20sign-ups%20in%20countries%20where%20it's%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ad%20plan%20first%20launched%2C%20the%20company%20cautioned%20investors%20that%20growth%20would%20be%20slow.%20Those%20days%20are%20over.%20Netflix%20told%20analysts%20it%20doubled%20its%20ad%20revenue%20in%202024%20and%20expects%20to%20double%20it%20again%20in%202025%2C%20as%20it%20adopts%20tech%20that%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20advertisers%20to%20buy%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2025%20is%20the%20year%20we%20transition%20from%20crawl%20to%20walk%2C%26quot%3B%20co-CEO%20Greg%20Peters%20said%20on%20an%20analyst%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20era%20is%20still%20a%20relatively%20new%20one%20for%20Netflix.%20For%20most%20of%20its%20history%2C%20it%20eschewed%20advertising.%20That%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-netflix-search-for-new-ads-leader-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanged%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20reported%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-earnings-losing-subscribers-second-straight-quarter-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubscription%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20that%20rattled%20investors.%20The%20ads%20plan%20has%20helped%20the%20company%20return%20to%20growth%20and%20cement%20its%20place%20as%20the%20king%20of%20the%20streamers%2C%20with%20more%20than%20300%20million%20global%20subscribers.%20It's%20also%20why%20Netflix%20has%20introduced%20more%20li