p%3EThe%2027%20states%20Live%20Nation%20is%20seeking%20to%20remove%20from%20the%20case%20are%20seeking%20triple%20monetary%20damages%20on%20the%20argument%20that%20their%20residents%20have%20been%20injured%20by%20the%20inflated%20ticket%20prices%20resulting%20from%20this%20lack%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20arguments%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-new-judge-sex-trafficking-ticketmaster-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20District%20Court%20Judge%20Arun%20Subramanian%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Live%20Nation%20attorney%20said%20concertgoers%20are%20too%20far%20removed%20from%20the%20alleged%20monopolistic%20conduct%20for%20states%20to%20sue%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20such%20an%20attenuated%20chain%20of%20causation%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20ticket%20consumer%20and%20any%20exclusivity%20deals%20involving%20artists%2C%20promoters%2C%20and%20venues%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20inefficient%20for%20the%20states%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bpiggybacking%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20federal%20goverment's%20claims%20over%20the%20exact%20same%20conduct%2C%20Live%20Nation%20also%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20downplaying%20the%20idea%20that%20competition%20would%20cut%20ticket%20prices%20as%20just%20%26quot%3Ba%20theory%2C%26quot%3B%20Gass%20offered%20the%20judge%20a%20hypothetical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20Live%20Nation%20allowed%20its%20rival%20promoters%20to%20bid%20for%20access%20to%20its%20amphitheaters%2C%20the%20lawyer%20told%20the%20judge.%20Rival%20promoter%20%26quot%3BA%26quot%3B%20would%20then%20offer%20Live%20Nation%20a%20sizable%20cut%20of%20its%20profits%2C%20only%20to%20be%20outbid%20by%20rival%20promoter%20%26quot%3BB%26quot%3B%20offering%20an%20even%20bigger%20cut.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20the%20price%20of%20the%20event%20goes%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Gass%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20voiced%20some%20skepticism.%3C