%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20investment%20group%20led%20by%20Shvo%20bought%20three%20adjacent%20historic%20Art%20Deco%20hotels%2C%20the%20Raleigh%2C%20the%20Richmond%2C%20and%20the%20South%20Seas%2C%20along%20the%20Miami%20Beach%20waterfront%20in%202019%20to%20amass%20the%20current%20development%20site.%20He%20paid%20roughly%20%24243%20million%20for%20the%20properties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShvo%20planned%20to%20renovate%20and%20redevelop%20the%20sites%20and%20tapped%20Rosewood%2C%20an%20upscale%20Hong%20Kong-based%20hospitality%20operator%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20new%20hotel%20and%20residences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20help%20publicize%20the%20project%2C%20Shvo%20installed%20an%20elaborate%20temporary%20garden%20of%20lush%20plantings%20and%20fanciful%20animal%20sculptures%20by%20the%20late%20French%20artists%20Claude%20and%20Fran%C3%A7ois-Xavier%20Lalanne.%20And%20he%20held%20upscale%20dinner%20parties%20catered%20by%20the%20renowned%20Italian%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erestaurant%20Langosteria%2C%20which%20has%20said%20it%20will%20open%20its%20first%20American%20outpost%20at%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20early%20buzz%20and%20luxury%20pedigree%2C%20preliminary%20site%20work%20had%20never%20progressed%20into%20full-bore%20construction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20hurdle%20Shvo%20has%20appeared%20to%20face%20are%20pre-sales%20at%20the%20sky-high%20values%20he%20has%20sought%20to%20achieve%20at%20the%20planned%20condo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20prerequisite%20to%20securing%20a%20loan%20large%20enough%20to%20fund%20construction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20developer%20has%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-P1jbB05bXc%26t%3D2159s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublicly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20has%20secured%20roughly%20%24250%20million%20of%20pre-sales%20at%20the%20condo%20buil